"{\"uid\": \"gbnews.com-news-video-debate-get-fiery-over-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony\", \"text\": \"ByGabrielle Wilde,  Published: 28/07/2024  Updated: 28/07/2024  Drag queens parodied Leonardo da Vinci's depiction of The Last Supper during the Opening Ceremony of the 2024 Paris Olympics  A debate on GB News got heated when Dr Sheikh Ramzy said that as a Muslim, he was \\\"offended\\\" by the depiction of the Christian painting, The Last Supper, at the Paris Olympic opening ceremony where it was reimagined by drag queens.  The reenactment of the famous painting, that shows Jesus's last meal with his disciples, was the centre of a backlash with Christians expressing their anger at the organisers of the Games.  READ THE FULL STORY HERE\"}"